snippet.title: Farming Slime Poop! | SLIME RANCHER | Fan Choice Friday
snippet.description:
Slime Rancher is a super-cute and fun game on Steam! You guys have been asking me to play it a TON the past 3 weeks, so here it is!

‚û° About My Channel
Hey everyone, it's your friend Thinknoodles and welcome to my YouTube channel! Join me, my dog Kopi and other friends on our adventures in video games. Here you can find all kinds of family-friendly gaming videos. I play lots of different games from Minecraft, Subnautica, FNaF World, Undertale and Super Mario Maker to your favorites or just plain random mobile games, indie games and more!

Some of my most popular series includes my Minecraft Mod series - Think's Lab - where I roleplay with my Minions and my Minecraft Survival Series - The Noodle Planet. I love all things gaming and bringing you great content that the whole family can enjoy.

Noodle on, Noodlers!
